    <Type>General</Type>
    <Text>A unique architecture, towering over the Chao Phraya River, makes it different with every imaginable scenery of city and river. Perfectly located within a walking distance to Silom and Sathon Road, Centre Point Silom offers you the utmost in comfort, style and elegance with various apartment types and excellent business and leisure facilities. Complete business facilities such as in-room Internet, conference rooms and a business center. Relax with the beautiful view of Chao Praya River and enjoy exercising in a fullly equipped fitness center, swimming pool and sauna room. Relax with the beautiful view of Chao Praya River and find a full range of facilities we provide to meet your lifestyles. Keep fit and fresh using our swimming pool, full-equipped fitness center and sauna room.</Text>
